WEBVTT

00:01:27.709 --> 00:01:32.341
Tiroîd kengî û çiqas hormonan çêke,

00:01:32.341 --> 00:01:35.816
Petûetêrî birêve dibe.

00:01:35.816 --> 00:01:39.250
Dema hormonên tiroîd di xwînê de

00:01:39.250 --> 00:01:40.807
kêm an zêde dibin

00:01:40.807 --> 00:01:43.234
hîpofîz bi hormona xwe TSH

00:01:43.234 --> 00:01:46.651
li tiroîd ferman dike û rast dike.

00:01:46.651 --> 00:01:49.020
Di vê pergala de jî,

00:01:49.020 --> 00:01:51.944
carinan pirsgirek derdikevin.

00:01:51.944 --> 00:01:53.230
Hin nexweşî,

00:01:53.230 --> 00:01:54.580
wek mezinbûna tiroîd,

00:01:54.580 --> 00:01:58.342
û bê ahengîyên kîmyevî, tiroîd şaş dikin,

00:01:58.342 --> 00:02:02.041
û tiroîd ji qontrala hîpofîz derdikeve.